9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode 15=

11
00:00:42,520 --> 00:00:43,439
It wasn't me!

12
00:00:44,759 --> 00:00:46,159
Father did it!

13
00:00:48,799 --> 00:00:49,719
Explain yourself.

14
00:00:49,840 --> 00:00:50,679
What happened?

15
00:00:52,439 --> 00:00:53,679
The Shadow Bureau's massacre

16
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:58,119
was just his way
of manipulating the court.

17
00:00:59,159 --> 00:01:00,439
What could I have done?

18
00:01:00,479 --> 00:01:01,280
So,

19
00:01:01,840 --> 00:01:03,560
your old man controls the bureau.

20
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:05,200
Yiyi, I'm sorry.

21
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:06,879
So that scent on you

22
00:01:08,359 --> 00:01:10,239
came from him.

23
00:01:12,159 --> 00:01:13,719
You're aiding a tyrant in his cruelty.

24
00:01:14,439 --> 00:01:15,640
You deserve to be punished!

25
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:24,920
Good strike.

26
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:27,599
I owe you that much.

27
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:30,680
Even as a pawn, you're pathetic.

28
00:01:33,079 --> 00:01:34,680
Then I'll spare your life

29
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:37,000
so you can watch yourself
lose everything.

30
00:01:47,359 --> 00:01:48,319
(Old man,)

31
00:01:49,079 --> 00:01:50,719
(tonight is your death sentence.)

32
00:01:50,879 --> 00:01:51,680
You hurt someone,

33
00:01:52,239 --> 00:01:53,319
then acted again

34
00:01:53,319 --> 00:01:54,560
without telling me.

35
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:58,680
You really don't take
my words seriously.

36
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:03,000
I didn't kill anyone.

37
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:05,319
Just collected some interest.

38
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:15,000
Mei Lin,

39
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:18,120
I promise I will avenge you.

40
00:02:19,039 --> 00:02:20,479
Whatever you want,

41
00:02:20,759 --> 00:02:22,080
I'll give it to you.

42
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,479
Your Highness,

43
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,280
it's my revenge.

44
00:02:29,759 --> 00:02:31,080
I should do it myself.

45
00:02:53,439 --> 00:02:54,919
Once this is over,

46
00:02:56,719 --> 00:03:00,639
I promise you a lifetime together,
just the two of us.

47
00:03:03,580 --> 00:03:05,060
ظآزWings of light drift through the airظآز

48
