74
00:04:48,279 --> 00:04:50,160
Issue the elite kill order.

75
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:52,199
Kill Pei Du, Minister of Judicature.

76
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:55,160
Whoever succeeds will be set free.

77
